Author: Malti#3948
Content:
The atomicDEX mobile beta program successfully launched on iOS and android and you can now join us in #atomicdex-beta - We want to celebrate this big release with the first part of a special DEX campaign. Post a fancy atomicDEX mobile photo of you or trading screenshot and we will randomly tip you some KMD out of a 777 KMD pot - use one from the below scenarios:

a) Tweet a photo of yourself with atomicDEX mobile running on your phone (showing your KMD QR code - or post the KMD address in a 2nd tweet-comment)  from a cool location 
b) Tweet a screenshot of a successful atomicDEX mobile RICK/MORTY swap and one with your KMD address QR code (from within atomicDEX mobile) - add some info ref. your experience to the tweet
c) Tweet a video of you using atomicDEX mobile (the coolest video gets on our official channels and blogs)

Please use hashtags #dex-it #atomicdex #DEX and tag us in the tweets (@komodoplatform) - share your tweets in the #talk-general and #dex-it channels. Happy beta!

https://atomicdex.io/
